Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.72,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}站起來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:04:02.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風が身を裂いても　待ってられない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:04:02.30,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算風撕碎身體 也不能再等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:07.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}絶望の果ての真実　求め
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:07.73,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追尋着絕望盡頭的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
